"等を、サービス向上・調査・学術研究等のために本サイト運営組織と当該コンペティ"
"ション主催者が利用することがあります。"
msgstr ""
"Data uploaded by users (predictions, models, analysis results, etc.), "
"operation history, etc. may be used by the organization operating this site "
"and the relevant competition organizer for service improvement, research, "
"academic research, etc. "

